Malaika Arora is an Indian actress, model, dancer, and television personality. She has been part of several successful item songs in Bollywood, including "Chaiyya Chaiyya" from the film "Dil Se" (1998) and "Munni Badnaam Hui" from the film "Dabangg" (2010). She has also been a judge on reality television shows in India, including "Nach Baliye" and "India's Got Talent."
